theory: iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('>'(PetalLength, 4.8), in(PetalWidth, [1.1, 1.6])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, versicolor) :- '>'(PetalLength, 4.8). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('=<'(PetalLength, 4.8), '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1)). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, setosa) :- '=<'(PetalLength, 4.8). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- true

iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('=<'(PetalLength, 3.6), '>'(PetalWidth, 1.1)). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, setosa) :- '=<'(PetalLength, 3.6). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- ('>'(PetalLength, 3.6), not_in(PetalLength, [3.6, 4.8]), in(PetalWidth, [1.1, 1.6])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, versicolor) :- ('>'(PetalLength, 3.6), not_in(PetalLength, [3.6, 4.8])). iris(PetalLength, PetalWidth, SepalLength, SepalWidth, virginica) :- true
